%
( A simple O sub example )

(Subroutine:  drill 3x 1" deep holes 1" apart along X)
O2000                        (O2000 sub)    (subroutine 2000)
G90 G99 G81 Z-1.0 R0.25                     (abs drill)
G91 G99 G81 X1 Z-1.25 R0 L2                 (drill two more holes 1" apart on X)
M99                          (O2000 endsub) (return)

(main program)
(- drill two rows of holes starting at X0.5 Y0.5 and then X0.5 Y1.5)
F40
G90 G0 Z0.25                                (abs jog to X0 Y0 Z0.25)
G0 X0.5 Y0.5
M98 P2000                    (O2000 call)   (drill three holes at Y0.5)
G90 G0 X0.5 Y1.5                            (abs jog to X0 Y1)
M98 P2000                    (O2000 call)   (drill three holes at Y1.5)
M30                                         (end)
%
